---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import DocsLayout from "../../components/docs/DocsLayout.svelte";

const tocItems = [
	{ label: "Features", href: "#features", level: 1 },
	{ label: "Sponsors", href: "#sponsors", level: 1 },
	{ label: "Acknowledgements", href: "#acknowledgements", level: 1 },
];
---

<Layout title="Introduction">
	<DocsLayout
		currentPath="/docs"
		tocItems={tocItems}
		githubUrl="https://github.com/saas-js/saas-ui-svelte"
		client:load
	>
		<div class="flex flex-col pb-4 gap-4">
			<h1 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight leading-7">
				Introduction
			</h1>
			<p class="text-fg-muted">
				SaaS UI Svelte is an open-source design system for building modern web applications with a native, high-quality feel.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="text-sm">
			<p class="text-fg-muted leading-relaxed mb-3.5">
				Inspired by macOS and premium tools like Linear, Attio, and Superhuman, it provides intuitive primitives
				that empower developers to create beautiful, user-friendly interfaces without sacrificing development velocity.
			</p>
			<p class="text-fg-muted leading-relaxed my-3.5">
				Whether you're building a simple dashboard or a complex enterprise application, SaaS UI Svelte helps you deliver polished experiences that users love.
			</p>

			<h2 id="features" class="text-lg font-semibold leading-6 tracking-tight mt-7 mb-3.5 scroll-mt-20">
				<a class="underline underline-offset-[3px] font-medium decoration-border-default hover:decoration-fg-default" href="#features">
					Features
				</a>
			</h2>
			<ul class="mt-3.5 mb-7 pl-5 list-disc">
				<li class="my-3 pl-1.5 text-fg-muted">
					<strong class="text-fg-default">Built for Svelte 5</strong> - Leveraging runes and snippets for optimal performance and developer experience.
				</li>
				<li class="my-3 pl-1.5 text-fg-muted">
					<strong class="text-fg-default">Accessible by default</strong> - All components follow WAI-ARIA guidelines using Ark UI primitives.
				</li>
				<li class="my-3 pl-1.5 text-fg-muted">
					<strong class="text-fg-default">Beautiful design</strong> - Carefully crafted components inspired by premium SaaS applications.
				</li>
				<li class="my-3 pl-1.5 text-fg-muted">
					<strong class="text-fg-default">Dark mode ready</strong> - Built-in support for light and dark themes.
				</li>
				<li class="my-3 pl-1.5 text-fg-muted">
					<strong class="text-fg-default">Fully customisable</strong> - Extend and modify components to match your brand.
				</li>
			</ul>

			<h2 id="sponsors" class="text-lg font-semibold leading-6 tracking-tight mt-7 mb-3.5 scroll-mt-20">
				<a class="underline underline-offset-[3px] font-medium decoration-border-default hover:decoration-fg-default" href="#sponsors">
					Sponsors
				</a>
			</h2>
			<ul class="mt-3.5 mb-7 pl-5 list-disc">
				<li class="my-3 pl-1.5">
					<a class="underline underline-offset-[3px] font-medium decoration-border-default hover:decoration-fg-default" href="https://github.com/ffaubert">Frank Faubert</a>
				</li>
				<li class="my-3 pl-1.5">
					<a class="underline underline-offset-[3px] font-medium decoration-border-default hover:decoration-fg-default" href="https://appulse.net/">Appulse Software</a>
				</li>
			</ul>

			<h2 id="acknowledgements" class="text-lg font-semibold leading-6 tracking-tight mt-7 mb-3.5 scroll-mt-20">
				<a class="underline underline-offset-[3px] font-medium decoration-border-default hover:decoration-fg-default" href="#acknowledgements">
					Acknowledgements
				</a>
			</h2>
			<p class="leading-relaxed text-fg-muted">
				SaaS UI Svelte is built with the help of many amazing libraries and their authors, without them this wouldn't be possible.
			</p>
			<ul class="mt-3.5 mb-7 pl-5 list-disc">
				<li class="my-3 pl-1.5 text-fg-muted">
					<a class="text-fg-default underline underline-offset-[3px] font-medium decoration-border-default hover:decoration-fg-default" href="https://svelte.dev/">Svelte</a> - The reactive framework powering our components.
				</li>
				<li class="my-3 pl-1.5 text-fg-muted">
					<a class="text-fg-default underline underline-offset-[3px] font-medium decoration-border-default hover:decoration-fg-default" href="https://ark-ui.com/">Ark UI</a> - Headless UI primitives providing accessibility and behaviour.
				</li>
				<li class="my-3 pl-1.5 text-fg-muted">
					<a class="text-fg-default underline underline-offset-[3px] font-medium decoration-border-default hover:decoration-fg-default" href="https://phosphoricons.com/">Phosphor Icons</a> - Beautiful, flexible icon family.
				</li>
				<li class="my-3 pl-1.5 text-fg-muted">
					<a class="text-fg-default underline underline-offset-[3px] font-medium decoration-border-default hover:decoration-fg-default" href="https://tailwindcss.com/">Tailwind CSS</a> - Utility-first CSS framework for styling.
				</li>
				<li class="my-3 pl-1.5 text-fg-muted">
					<a class="text-fg-default underline underline-offset-[3px] font-medium decoration-border-default hover:decoration-fg-default" href="https://saas-ui.dev/">SaaS UI</a> - The original React design system that inspired this port.
				</li>
			</ul>

			<div class="flex items-center pb-20 mt-20 gap-8">
				<div class="flex-1"></div>
				<a class="flex-1 px-3 py-2 border rounded-md border-border-default hover:border-border-emphasized transition-colors" href="/docs/components/button">
					<div class="flex flex-col text-sm text-end gap-1 leading-5">
						<p class="text-fg-muted">
							Next
						</p>
						<div class="inline-flex items-center justify-end font-medium gap-2">
							Components
							<svg stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-3.5 fill-none stroke-current">
								<path d="m9 18 6-6-6-6"></path>
							</svg>
						</div>
					</div>
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</DocsLayout>
</Layout>
